NOTE: If you are looking for a C HTML templating library then may I suggest
you take a look at libflate (https://github.com/ac000/libflate) instead.

It is licensed under the LGPL 2.1 and I think it has a nicer HTML templating
syntax.

I was using libctemplte but have since switched to libflate.


Overview
========

This is libctemplate, a C HTML Template Library from

	http://libctemplate.sourceforge.net/

written by: Stephen C. Losen, University of Virginia

It is released under the GNU General Public License version 3
